NAME
    MooX::LazyRequire - Required attributes which fail only when trying to
    use them

SYNOPSIS
      package MyClass;
      use Moo;
      use MooX::LazyRequire;

      has attr => ( is => 'rw', lazy_required => 1 );

DESCRIPTION
    MooX::LazyRequire creates attributes that are required, but will fail on
    use rather that on object creation.

SEE ALSO
    MooseX::LazyRequire

AUTHOR
